- GitHub Actions:
    - Build, run tests, run snapshots on iOS latest.
    - Lint/format check (SwiftFormat/SwiftLint if used).
    - Upload coverage (xcresult + slather/codecov).
- On tag, create a GitHub Release with the .ipa/.xcarchive artifact.
- Add PR template and Conventional Commits check.
- Fail build on coverage drop or lint errors.